#<AdxTL>@(#)0.0.0.0 $Revision$
# Superviseur
# Gestion du masque TNH2 

$_AFF
If GIMPORT
 Gosub AFF From GSAISIE
Else
 If GMESSAGE <>""
  Gosub ERR From GSAISIE
 Else
  Raz GERR , GZNUM
 Endif
Endif
Return

$HORODAT
Local Date    A_DATE
Local Char    A_HEURE(10) , A_USER(10)
Local Char    A_STAMP(15)
A_DATE  = [09/11/2018]
A_HEURE = "23:06:49"
A_USER  = "DOC"
A_STAMP = "20181109230649"
Return

$TITRES
Return

$VISU
Local Integer A_REPONSE
Global Integer GPRE_VIEW
If dim(A_WINDPREV)<=0 : Local Char A_WINDPREV(30) : Endif
Local Mask TNH2 [TNH2]
Gosub HORODAT
Local Inpbox "TNH2" From GFONCTION At A_STAMP With A_WINDPREV Mask [TNH2] As [SIM_]
Grizo [TNH2]10
Grizo [TNH2]20
Grizo [TNH2]30
Grizo [TNH2]40
Boxact [SIM_]
Gosub TITRES
Boxinp [SIM_] Using A_REPONSE
Close Local Inpbox [SIM_]
Close Local Mask [TNH2]
Kill GPRE_VIEW
Return

$HARDCOP
Local Integer X1(0..14),X2(0..14),Y1(0..14),Y2(0..14)
X1(0)=1 : X2(0)=84 : Y1(0)=1 : Y2(0)=4
X1(1)=1 : X2(1)=84 : Y1(1)=5 : Y2(1)=9
X1(2)=1 : X2(2)=84 : Y1(2)=10 : Y2(2)=11
X1(3)=1 : X2(3)=84 : Y1(3)=12 : Y2(3)=21
Return

$ON_DPEDAT
Onevent CONTROL Call C_DPEDAT(zc) From W1TNH2
Onevent AFTER_CHANGE Gosub AMM_DPEDAT From W1TNH2
Onevent BEFORE_AREA Gosub AV_DPEDAT From W1TNH2
Return

$AV_DPEDAT
Chgfmt [M]DPEDAT(indice) With "DZ:"+GFMDAT
Gosub _AFF
Return

Subprog C_DPEDAT(VALEUR)
Variable Date    VALEUR
## Action STD
Call C_DPEDAT(VALEUR) From SUBTNH
If mkstat : GERR = 1 : GZONE = "DPEDAT" : GZNUM = 52763 : Endif
Gosub _AFF
End

$AMM_DPEDAT
Call AM_DPEDAT(zc)
If !mkstat & GOBJET
 zoncou = "DPEDAT" : Gosub APRES_MODIF From =GPROGRAMME
Endif
Return

Subprog AM_DPEDAT(VALEUR)
Variable Date    VALEUR
## Action STD
Call AM_DPEDAT(VALEUR) From SUBTNH
If mkstat : GERR = 1 : GZONE = "DPEDAT" : GZNUM = 52763 : Endif
Gosub _AFF
End

